CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Rani Therapeutics Holdings Inc is a clinical stage biotherapeutics company advancing technologies to enable the development of orally administered biologics. The company has developed the RaniPill capsule, a proprietary and patented platform technology, intended to replace subcutaneous or IV injection of biologics with oral dosing.
